sney+ in Spectrum TV Select, and ESPN+ in Spectrum TV Select Plus=E2=80=94o=
n to the company=E2=80=99s systems. But several sources have told me that t=
he Disney streaming products have performed poorly so far for Charter, with=
 take rate for both apps way down in the single digits. Sure, it=E2=80=99s =
early days, and the very notion of cable operators offering streaming apps =
