really marketed them to consumers, though I expect those efforts to ramp up=
 when
it adds more services, like Paramount+ (later this year) and ESPN Flagship =
(next year). But it=E2=80=99s also possible that streaming is just simply n=
ot a good substitute for the cable bundle, especially among older subscribe=
rs. If these numbers stay low, they have the potential to swing negotiating=
