ublican National Convention and <b>Trump</b>=E2=80=99s selection of <b>J.D.=
 Vance </b>as his vice presidential running mate. But it=E2=80=99s MLB All-=
Star week here at The Varsity! Happy Home Run Derby Day to all who celebrat=
e. <br/><br/>I=E2=80=99m coming to you live from Arlington, Texas, the home=
 of tonight=E2=80=99s festivities and tomorrow=E2=80=99s midsummer classic.=
 Thus far, every conversation around here has coalesced around the slow but=
